      <title>两艘驶往萨哈林岛的俄罗斯油轮未能运送货物</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/two-russian-oil-tankers-critical-to-sakhalin-fail-to-move-cargo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两艘用于运输俄罗斯萨哈林岛 2 号项目原油的穿梭油轮自 4 月份以来一直无法运输货物，导致全部运输负担都落在了一艘船上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/two-russian-oil-tankers-critical-to-sakhalin-fail-to-move-cargo</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 10:31:36 GMT</pubDate>
